                                  DISCLAIMER
       The Public Employment Relations Board maintains this web site to
     enhance public access to PERB's information. This is a service that
          is continually under development. While we try to keep the
     information timely and accurate, we make no guarantees. We will make
        an effort to correct errors brought to our attention. Persons
         utilizing this site are encouraged to verify the information
         described herein by reading the text of the Board decisions
                                 themselves.

